body:
This mod automatically allows most non-solid vanilla blocks to be waterlogged with any existing placeable fluid.  
&nbsp;  
It also provides an API that other mods can make use of to make their own blocks able to be fluid-logged.  
&nbsp;  
Blocks in other mods that extend from compatible vanilla blocks will automatically be able to be fluid-logged.  
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
Notes for Multiplayer:  
- While having this mod installed on only the server is technically possible, it is recommended for the client to have it installed as well, otherwise visual desync may occur.  

- Ensure that when connecting to a server, the client is using the same config as the server.  

&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
Removing mods that add new fluids will remove that fluid from existing fluid-logged blocks.  
&nbsp;  
Removing this mod will remove all fluids from existing non-waterloggable blocks, while keeping vanilla waterlogged blocks intact.
